                                     Table "public.users"
    Column    |              Type              | Collation | Nullable |        Default         
--------------+--------------------------------+-----------+----------+------------------------
 id           | text                           |           | not null | 
 email        | text                           |           | not null | 
 passwordHash | text                           |           | not null | 
 fullName     | text                           |           | not null | 
 role         | "UserRole"                     |           | not null | 
 status       | "UserStatus"                   |           | not null | 'ACTIVE'::"UserStatus"
 collegeId    | text                           |           |          | 
 publisherId  | text                           |           |          | 
 lastLoginAt  | timestamp(3) without time zone |           |          | 
 createdAt    | timestamp(3) without time zone |           | not null | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 updatedAt    | timestamp(3) without time zone |           | not null | 
 departmentId | text                           |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "users_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "users_collegeId_idx" btree ("collegeId")
    "users_departmentId_idx" btree ("departmentId")
    "users_email_idx" btree (email)
    "users_email_key" UNIQUE, btree (email)
    "users_publisherId_idx" btree ("publisherId")
    "users_role_idx" btree (role)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "users_collegeId_fkey" FOREIGN KEY ("collegeId") REFERENCES colleges(id) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE SET NULL
    "users_publisherId_fkey" FOREIGN KEY ("publisherId") REFERENCES publishers(id) ON UPDATE CASCADE ON DELETE SET NULL
